        <in:em>[Section 12 (a)]</in:em>
      </bcl:centertext>
      <bcl:indent1>
        <in:strong>1</in:strong> An operator must ensure that an industrial camp providing accommodation for the number of persons set out in Column 1 has at least the fixtures set out in Columns 2 to 4 opposite the number of persons.</bcl:indent1>
      <bcl:indent1>
